text: Brown Boy 2 is a commercial mixtape by Canadian rapper Nav, released on May 11, 2020. The mixtape was released as the deluxe edition of his third studio album Good Intentions, which was released three days prior, on May 8, 2020. The mixtape also serves as the sequel to Nav's 2019 EP Brown Boy. It comprises 14 tracks, and includes guest appearances from Quavo and Lil Duke. The deluxe edition contributed to Good Intentions debut at number one on the Billboard 200. ==Background== Nav described Brown Boy 2 as containing "some snippets, some leaks and some new vibes". ==Track listing== Credits adapted from Tidal, and Nav's Instagram for the deluxe edition.
